data.title: Newark Airport Rail Station
data.meta_description: New Jersey Public Transportation Corporation - The Way To Go
data.text:
Newark International Airport Station

There is no direct bus service to or from this station. Train service is available from this station to and from Newark Penn Station where connections are available to interstate bus service, Greyhound, and local bus routes.

There is no parking or pick-up / drop-off location at this station. Customers may board AirTrain at the station for service to the airport terminals., Newark, NJ,
